

 INTRO,DENTRO,FUCKTRO - that all you could see...

        But I hope you've never seen FRACTRO
                                    ~~~~~~~~~
                 I made it, because I wanted to try to make a 4K-intro.


This is a non-AGA intro for MC68000. You can run it:
 1) from Shell    - type "fractro.exe" (but you have to be in PAL).
 2) from icon.AGA - for owners of multiscan monitors or if you work in NTSC
                      or VGA (script contains killAGA)
 3) from icon.OCS


Tested: A1200  6MB RAM
        A500   1MB RAM



Special greets to:  Mr. Quido
                    Michael Blajic
                    Abbe
                    Jofa & Trixie

Normal greets to: All coders in Opava


                                        coded at 12-Jun-96 
                                        by Little Green
                                        in Opava, Cz

      Feel The Power Of Pure Code !



A pro Cechy:
  Prvni efektik (takove ty ozrane pismenka) by vypadal pekne hnusne, kdybych
to kresli z obycejnych fill-lajn. Proto jsem kazdou caru nahradil osmi
jinyma podle algoritmu na rekurzivni presouvani prostredniho bodu
od nejakeho Norberta Weinera podle RND generatoru
(neboli er en degeneratoru  (add.w  $dff006,RND) ).
  Druhy kousek je tzv. snehova vlocka nejake Helgy von Koch, kdy se  na 
misto druhe tretiny usecky postavi rovnostranny trojuhelnik. V prvni vlocce
ven, ve druhe dovnitr.
  No a ta mapa je delana na uplne stejnem principu jako efektik 1 (ale je
synteticka, protoze tam je nekde chyba).
  
Ptate se, odkud jsem tak chytrej? 
    Mno, Michael mi pujcil chytrou knizku, jinak by me nenapadlo tohleto
cele vubec delat.
